# Model assets bundled with libsixel

This directory keeps model artifacts that can be bundled alongside libsixel.
The repository layout mirrors the installation structure so downstream tooling
can rely on a stable path even when no runtime feature consumes these assets.

The expected installation root remains `share/libsixel/models` to preserve
package layout compatibility.

Please consult the main `LICENSE` file for any upstream license text tied to
bundled assets.
